ENC003: Does your company encrypt all applicable confidential data and media (data at rest, in transit, removable media, backups, etc.) using an acceptable encryption method?

If yes, please describe any tools used and encryption algorithms/strength.
Artifact Required:  
Evidence showing encryption of removable media;
Evidence validating data is encrypted at rest in databases;
Evidence validating data is encrypted at rest in disk storage;
Evidence validating backup data and tapes is encrypted
